WEBVTT

1
00:00:22.050 --> 00:00:23.700
别介
Don't

2
00:00:26.400 --> 00:00:28.575
我说别介
I said "Don't"

3
00:00:29.375 --> 00:00:30.075
谁呀？
Who's this?

4
00:00:32.200 --> 00:00:33.025
是上帝吗？
Are you God?

5
00:00:34.475 --> 00:00:36.800
我是中国人，所以你肯定是如来
I'm Chinese, so you must be Buddha.

6
00:00:38.725 --> 00:00:43.800
但我在美国，所以你肯定是耶... 耶... 耶稣!
But I'm in the US, so you must be Je... Jesus... Jesus Christ!

7
00:00:45.700 --> 00:00:48.125
我觉得如来肯定不会说英文
I don't think Buddha speaks English.

8
00:00:48.550 --> 00:00:50.275
告诉我把我的小男孩儿
So tell me little boy,

9
00:00:50.275 --> 00:00:54.875
为什么你试图在如此美好的一天自杀？
why are you trying to commit suicide on such a glorious day?

10
00:00:55.350 --> 00:01:00.000
因为一切都再也没有意义了
Cause everything just doesn't make sense anymore.

11
00:01:04.100 --> 00:01:08.025
一年，我特么用了一整年做的这个APP，
A year, I spent a whole fucking year building this APP,

12
00:01:08.725 --> 00:01:11.950
到现在一个人也不愿意用
and now, not even a single person wants to use it.

13
00:01:13.200 --> 00:01:14.225
太悲哀了！
So pathetic!

14
00:01:14.800 --> 00:01:19.575
有点儿意思，那这个APP是干嘛用的呀？
Interesting, so what does this APP do?

15
00:01:21.125 --> 00:01:24.675
是一款通过看电影来学英语的APP
It's an APP for learning English by watching movies you know.

16
00:01:25.350 --> 00:01:31.250
它有这么一个让你感觉就像在和演员用英语对话一样的聊天模式
It has this amazing "Chat Mode" which makes you feel like you're talking with the actors using English.

17
00:01:32.300 --> 00:01:38.025
而且这个APP前所未有地提供了所有能让你能更好理解电影的信息
And the app provides all the information you need to fully understand the movie, like never before.

18
00:01:39.575 --> 00:01:43.900
比如语法、文化背景、冷知识
You know things like grammar, cultural references, trivia.

19
00:01:44.475 --> 00:01:46.325
我意思是，这多棒啊！
I mean, how awesome this is!

20
00:01:46.800 --> 00:01:49.875
好吧，听起来确实不错
Well, it sounds pretty good indeed.

21
00:01:50.425 --> 00:01:57.025
这样如何？我会让每个看这个视频的人都去下载这个APP，
How about this? I'll make everyone who will be watching this video download your APP,

22
00:01:57.025 --> 00:01:59.700
但是你得停止你这愚蠢的行为
but you need to stop this madness.

23
00:01:59.750 --> 00:02:02.225
狗呼嘛？你当真会那样做？
Really? Will you do that?

24
00:02:02.425 --> 00:02:04.200
会的，我的孩子
Yes, my son.

25
00:02:05.500 --> 00:02:06.600
我爱你，上帝！
I love you, God!

26
00:02:10.425 --> 00:02:12.125
我能... 我能再提一个愿望吗？
Can... Can I have one more wish?

27
00:02:12.425 --> 00:02:13.525
啥？
Uh-huh?

28
00:02:13.825 --> 00:02:15.375
你能升级一下我的电脑吗？
Can you upgrade my computer？

29
00:02:15.750 --> 00:02:18.425
噢，你能修一下我的车吗？
Oh... Can you fix my car?

30
00:02:18.950 --> 00:02:20.125
噢，等等，不不
Oh... Wait, no no.

31
00:02:21.325 --> 00:02:22.500
你能帮我找个女朋友吗？
Can you find me a girlfriend?

32
00:02:22.850 --> 00:02:24.450
女朋友？
A girlfriend?

33
00:02:24.700 --> 00:02:27.025
连我都没有个该死的女朋友！
Even I don't have a goddamn girlfriend!

34
00:02:27.175 --> 00:02:28.050
靠！
Damn it!

